### Change driver availability - set available
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/driver/1/availability?available=true
Accept: */*

### Change driver availability - set unavailable
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/driver/1/availability?available=false
Accept: */*

### Request driver logout - no active ride (should succeed)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/driver/1/request-logout?hasActiveRide=false
Accept: */*

### Request driver logout - active ride (should return 409)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/driver/1/request-logout?hasActiveRide=true
Accept: */*
